            <img src=/usr/share/skutter/icons/{2}.png valign="middle"/>
        </td>
        <td colspan="3" style="vertical-align:middle;">
            <span style="font-size:9pt;">Currently <font style="text-transform: lowercase;">{4}</font>.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's {3}°; the high today was forecast at {13}°, low at {12}°.</span><br>
